00:26:33.125 --> 00:26:36.708
I'm sure my unethical conduct

00:26:36.791 --> 00:26:38.750
- led to my daughter's tragic death.
- No.

00:26:38.833 --> 00:26:40.791
- Chao Ching--
- It's my karma.

