- No.
- Drink.

00:39:50.750 --> 00:39:52.250
Tell him to quiet down.

00:39:52.333 --> 00:39:54.000
- Okay. Go.
- Cup.

00:39:54.083 --> 00:39:55.291
Cup!

00:39:59.333 --> 00:40:00.333
Hurry, I'm thirsty.

00:40:04.166 --> 00:40:05.500
Go, go, go.

00:40:06.958 --> 00:40:08.083
Where's the ice?

00:40:09.000 --> 00:40:10.000
Ice!

