- Okay.
- What kind of place doesn’t use ice?

00:40:19.208 --> 00:40:22.833
How am I supposed to drink this?
Who sells drinks without ice?

00:40:23.500 --> 00:40:26.125
Hey! I want to drink something cold!

00:40:27.916 --> 00:40:29.000
I'm thirsty!

00:40:36.208 --> 00:40:38.500
Hurry up, I’m thirsty.

00:40:52.833 --> 00:40:53.833
Thank you.

00:40:55.375 --> 00:40:56.375
Bye!

00:41:05.750 --> 00:41:07.416
Oh, my God.

00:41:07.500 --> 00:41:09.166
Think he'll get diarrhea?

00:41:10.125 --> 00:41:11.125
Who cares?

00:42:33.500 --> 00:42:35.791
I can't. This kind of music makes me cry.

00:42:36.958 --> 00:42:39.125
Why would a song make you cry?

00:42:41.958 --> 00:42:43.958
I hardly ever see you cry.

00:42:44.041 --> 00:42:45.708
Of course I cry.

00:42:46.833 --> 00:42:47.833
When?

00:42:51.416 --> 00:42:52.625
When Hsin-yi died.

00:42:54.125 --> 00:42:55.125
And…

00:42:57.041 --> 00:42:58.458
when my husband died.

00:42:59.125 --> 00:43:01.375
I rarely hear you talk about your husband.

00:43:01.458 --> 00:43:04.833
It wasn't some passionate romance.
It's not worth mentioning.

00:43:06.916 --> 00:43:08.083
How did you two meet?

00:43:09.375 --> 00:43:12.708
He used to come to Kuala Lumpur for work.

00:43:13.291 --> 00:43:15.041
I thought he was quite nice.

00:43:15.125 --> 00:43:16.750
He gave me a sense of security.

00:43:16.833 --> 00:43:18.291
And then we got together.

00:43:18.833 --> 00:43:20.166
And then?

00:43:20.250 --> 00:43:23.000
I dropped everything,
got married and moved to Taiwan.

00:43:24.083 --> 00:43:25.458
Then what happened?

00:43:26.125 --> 00:43:28.833
I had Hsin-yi
and the three of us lived our lives.

00:43:28.916 --> 00:43:29.958
That's it.

00:43:32.541 --> 00:43:33.791
How did he die?

00:43:35.000 --> 00:43:35.916
Cancer.

00:43:44.458 --> 00:43:46.916
Ever since I learned about the Goddess,

00:43:47.000 --> 00:43:49.666
the person I wanted
to revive the most wasn't Hsin-yi.

00:43:50.666 --> 00:43:51.750
It was my husband.

00:43:53.166 --> 00:43:54.500
Why not Hsin-yi?

00:43:57.625 --> 00:44:00.208
Even if she was revived,
she'd only have seven days.

00:44:01.375 --> 00:44:03.666
The burden of knowing
your death is imminent

00:44:05.208 --> 00:44:06.708
is too cruel…

00:44:08.833 --> 00:44:09.916
for a young girl.

00:44:12.250 --> 00:44:15.208
But my husband was different.
He was amazing.

00:44:16.333 --> 00:44:18.333
When he found out he had cancer,

00:44:18.416 --> 00:44:21.000
the doctor told him
he had three months left.

00:44:21.083 --> 00:44:22.750
He actually kept it from me.

00:44:24.125 --> 00:44:25.833
He happily got on with life

00:44:25.916 --> 00:44:28.375
as if nothing had happened.

00:44:29.666 --> 00:44:32.000
Then one day, he passed out at home.

00:44:32.625 --> 00:44:35.208
I took him to the hospital and found out.

00:44:36.166 --> 00:44:37.625
After that,

00:44:38.458 --> 00:44:39.583
he never

00:44:41.166 --> 00:44:42.625
woke up again.

00:44:43.916 --> 00:44:46.583
I didn't get the chance
to speak to him one last time.

00:44:48.125 --> 00:44:49.625
Why did he keep it from you?

00:44:51.041 --> 00:44:53.333
He was probably worried
I couldn't take it.

00:44:54.583 --> 00:44:56.416
He kept working hard,

00:44:56.500 --> 00:44:59.500
hoping to save enough money
for me and Hsin-yi.

00:45:00.083 --> 00:45:01.750
So he refused treatment.

00:45:02.541 --> 00:45:05.375
Your husband was such a good man.

00:45:09.291 --> 00:45:11.041
But I couldn't fulfill his wishes.

00:45:11.666 --> 00:45:13.166
When he was dying,

00:45:13.958 --> 00:45:16.125
I spent all of our money on his treatment.

00:45:17.125 --> 00:45:20.166
Even my mother-in-law
urged me not to waste money.

00:45:20.250 --> 00:45:22.208
The doctor said his chances were slim.

00:45:22.916 --> 00:45:24.250
But I wouldn't listen.

00:45:25.666 --> 00:45:27.125
I wanted him to wake up.

00:45:31.708 --> 00:45:33.375
If he woke up,

00:45:33.458 --> 00:45:35.083
what would you say to him?

00:45:37.666 --> 00:45:39.666
I'd probably yell at him for a bit.

00:47:04.958 --> 00:47:07.916
If you can't help them, let them die.

00:47:11.375 --> 00:47:14.500
The Goddess says she cannot
feel the living's longing for him

00:47:14.583 --> 00:47:16.166
and cannot resurrect him.

00:47:16.250 --> 00:47:17.208
What?

00:47:17.291 --> 00:47:18.416
How can that be?

00:47:19.083 --> 00:47:20.041
Please leave.

00:47:20.125 --> 00:47:21.291
Goddess,

00:47:21.875 --> 00:47:23.500
please, try--

00:47:47.166 --> 00:47:48.166
